Notes: SP wins Surf N'Slam Classic...SP starts 11-0 for first time since 1976...PLN
led 31-29 before SP closed first half with 9-0 run over final 2:44...Game was
tied five times in first half...SP led 59-51 with 5:18 left and held PLN
without a field goal during a 13-2 run over next three minutes.
